title: Episode 15 - Rio 2016 Day 13 Review
itunes:title: Episode 15 - Rio 2016 Day 13 Review
description: Another episode where all we basically talk about is Usain Bolt and Ryan Lochte. One has gotten better, the other has gotten worse. Which order do you think that's in? Ben also discovers a new favourite sport, Colin discovers Canada are pretty awesome at the Summer Olympics and those epic fan messages keep coming.
